               <msContents>
                  <summary>The hymn, "God Reigns," ascribed to Zär’a Ya‘əqob, እግዚአብሔር፡ ነግሠ፡, Three Miracles of Mary, ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from = "1r" to = "72v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1325egziab"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id = "ms_i2"><locus from = "73r" to = "79r"/><title>Three Miracles of Mary</title>
                    <msItem xml:id = "ms_i2.1">
                      <locus from = "73r" to = "75r"/>
                      <title ref = "LIT3900Miracle"/>
                      </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                      <locus from = "75r" to = "78r"/>
                      <title>The man who was able to learn Hail Mary only, with incipit:
                        <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእነ፡ ቅድቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ማርያም፡...ወሀሎ፡ ፩መስተፅዕነ፡ ፈረስ፡ ኃጥእ፡ በኵሉ፡ ፍናዊሁ፡ ዓለማዊ። ወባሕቱ፡ ጸጋ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡...</foreign>
                        </title>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
                      <locus from = "78r" to = "79r"/>
                      <title ref = "LIT3597Miracle"/>
                    </msItem>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
